Wow,It's been just about two years since I wrote in this thing. Quite weird I must say. When I look back on when I first started writing in any kind of blog,well it was just fake. I wasn't expressing my true feelings,or was giving a G to PE rated version of how I really felt. So first off let me say,FUCK,I'm going to write how I feel when I feel it. Well give or take a few days depending if I feel lazy or not. Well I guess I should give an update on what's been happening in my life.

-First off,I needed Spring Break,but I have been so damn lazy. With AP tests in less than a month,I should really be studying,but I really don't feel like it. It seems to be my drive for school has been gone for awhile. I want to gradulate already,of course I'll miss my friends,but I just need a change.

-As for college,I'm going to UCLA,and I'm pretty sure I'll be rooming with Jeanie. Man to be honest,if you would have asked my Freshmen year if I would be friends with Jeanie,I just would have looked at you funny. I always thought in middle school she only cared about school work. Well I was completely wrong and I believe Jeanie has been one of the people I have ever been close with. Jeanie I know your going to read this so let me say I'm glad your my best friend,and I consider you like my sister. ^^

-Damn,I am one of those lame people that reflect all the time. Yes,I have been reflecting about High School. I can remember so much. FLASHBACKS!!!! Hmmm..memories lets see...

I always hated PE.

Kristi will always be my science buddy.

I will never regret mentioning Victor Baker touches himself,or waking him up in World History for that matter.

Terrence will always be the moody guy.

I will never like Dr.O,the man is a jerk.

I always have to remember dancing like an old blind man for one of Keaney's video.

I will always laugh when I think of the words squish squish,sparkles,and sluttybitch.

Well that is enough memories for now. I have gotten lazy again. I will try to write move,hopefully.

Hey hey people i'm posting from Pomona College and let me tell  you,The work is a bitch!!!!!I mean its fun but hell we got so much work that Jeanie was depressed!!!!!!!Other than that,its pretty cool.The t.a.'s are still cool but really loud!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!And yea Jeanie is scared of some of them.(lol).So summer has been crazy already and its only been 3 weeks.Well thank god that i dont have that much work tonight but other than that I just wanna go home right now.Field trip tomorrow!!!!!!(finally,one more  day of work and I would have shot someone.So cya later weirdo's!

Well what up people? Came back from Pomona College and let me tell you....crazy times...crazy times,lol.The work sucked but it's all good.I guess right now I feel so weird.Some of my friends like my other friends and it just feels weird.I mean nobody likes me in that way,I feel like I'm an ugly piece of crap but thats life.I mean its hard to focus on work sometimes when you want something else. I mean hell nobody has ever liked me,and if I told the guy liked about my feelings...he'll just laugh at me and tell his friends that are my friends as well.Like I said to some people...I guess i'm the ugly chick in honors.Well you can tell i'm in a downer mood.Peace Out people,I'm out,I guess I just need some sleep.
